We may also use your contact information to send you notifications regarding new services, offers and promotions offered by 'My Dictionary' if you affirmatively consent to receive such communications.
Profile information is used by 'My Dictionary' to be presented back to and edited by you when you access the Service and to be presented to other users. In some cases, other users may be able to supplement your profile, including by submitting comments (which can be deleted by you). 'My Dictionary' uses this information to provide you with support, to send you essential notifications, to enforce our terms, conditions and policies, to communicate with you, to administer the Services, and for internal operations, including troubleshooting, data analysis, testing, research, statistical, and survey purposes.
